{"tid":1806590,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家針對匯豐支線係咪應該諗清楚","createTime":"2020-01-01T11:15:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T12:14:10.000Z","uid":321504,"like":13,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f9322f8b38709116687a13124e386771f48bd575","tid":1806590,"uid":321504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:15:29.000Z","msg":"大家屌我之前真係希望睇清楚，諗一諗<br />\n<br />\n其實我記得星火啱啱畀人凍結 連登有人帶風裝修匯豐， 但好多人屌佢。 但其實匯豐作為一間商業銀行政府要佢封戶口， 佢冇嘢可以做到。 更何況封咗戶口之後其實匯豐開咗支票畀星火班人， 畀佢匯走啲錢。 耐何黑警運用公權力， 禁止匯款。 所以其實星火之仇應該係對準黑警。<br />\n<br />\n你可以話我分化撚， 忘恩負義， 但呢個就係事實。"},{"pid":"355f58f21999f6241346162900c9e6fea1fd8070","tid":1806590,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:17:16.000Z","msg":"［置頂］20:00 和你Shop x 黃圈：開飯啦！元旦促銷大減價 ！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1806464\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1806464</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8593aac3301a468ba5b43f40104760091b150485","tid":1806590,"uid":2676,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"下？匯豐今日開埋門比狗入去埋伏手足喎？"},{"pid":"b5d043b5bd8af066746925b4992a65c1a64ad3c0","tid":1806590,"uid":51790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:18:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">同意<br />\n都未裝修完中資就裝修hsbc<br />\n又俾人帶風向</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff0343f5f6ff3005b05a661db5c33fa7bb0fb82d","tid":1806590,"uid":133100,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8593aac3301a468ba5b43f40104760091b150485","tid":1806590,"uid":2676,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:18:49.000Z","msg":"下？匯豐今日開埋門比狗入去埋伏手足喎？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T11:51:44.000Z","msg":"埋伏? 即係hsbc今日擔心自己財產受破壞所以俾警方入去守住，跟住有人入去想破壞點知踩陷阱?"},{"pid":"b3a1565d87be522689eec00b8c1678494bbe331e","tid":1806590,"uid":321504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"